                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920215-40-off223 t17920215-40-cd224"></join>, one pair of leather half-boots, value 3 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17920215-40-victim491" type="victimName">
                     Baltis 
